        a       <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> , <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0008150> ;
        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>
                "SPOP:CUL3:RBX1 E3 ubiquitin ligase complex regulates the ubiquitination and degradation of PD-L1(CD274) protein. This is negatively regulated by Cyclin D:CDK4 complex which phosphorylates SPOP on Ser-6 (S6) and facilitates its sequestration by 14-3-3 protein gamma (Zhang et al., 2018), thus inhibiting SPOP-mediated recruitment in the E3 ubiquitin ligase complex." ;
        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>
